Adobe Names Jon Perera VP of Worldwide Education Marketing

-- B y   D a n   H a r t
-- 
2011-10-02T15:34:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-02/adobe-names-jon-perera-vp-of-worldwide-education-marketing.html
Adobe Systems Inc. (ADBE)  named Jon Perera
to the post of vice president of worldwide education marketing.
He joins the company from Microsoft Corp., where he was general
manager of its academic programs group.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Hart at 
 dahart@bloomberg.net  